This is a working directory of huggle, if you need to read the main
readme file, please open the repository root/README.md

If you downloaded this package using any other source than github,
or there is no such a file like README.md, here is at least the
minimal readme:

What is this
=============
Please read http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:HG

How to build:
=============

./configure 
make

Structure of this folder:
===========================
C++ code is all in this folder, because qmake doesn't like subfolders very much.

Other subfolders:

./Localizations - contains language files
./Resources - contains graphics and text files
./man - contains manual page
./hunker - contains hunker that patches the makefile

Please read the coding standards before you submit any new code to this
repository, they are located in root directory as well

